This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image classification tasks. It may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it proposes a new layer for deep neural networks. Additionally, it could belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category as it deals with improving the generalization ability of neural networks. The Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category is also a possibility as it deals with optimizing the neural network's performance. Finally, the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category is a possibility as it deals with image datasets.
